msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Sega - MS/GG/MD/CD (Genesis Plus GX)"
msgstr "Sega - MS/GG/MD/CD (Genesis Plus GX)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Genesis Plus GX is an enhanced port of Genesis Plus to the libretro API.[CR][CR]Features support for SG-1000, Mark-III, Master System, Game Gear, Mega Drive and Mega CD hardware."
msgstr "Genesis Plus GX je vylepšený port Genesis Plus pro API Libretro.[CR][CR]Podporuje hardware SG-1000, Mark-III, Master System, Game Gear, Mega Drive a Mega CD."

msgctxt "Addon Disclaimer"
msgid "Special thanks to twinaphex for backporting enhancements from the GX version"
msgstr "Zvláštní poděkování patří twinaphexovi za backportování vylepšení z verze GX"

